Innovation Corner
H-306 Tapping Sleeve
The new H-306 fabricated steel tapping sleeve is designed for hot tapping ductile iron pipe and thick-wall C900 plastic pipe. It features an integral bolt flange, Rilsan nylon coating, working pressures up to 300psi, and is available in 4”-16” sizes.






