Product Catalog








Mueller Canada

Since 1857, the Mueller® name has been associated with dependable water distribution products around the globe. With a foundation of solid core values and a clear mission, Mueller Canada serves as an extension of Mueller Company and its affiliates.View More >








Mueller® International Division

Since 1857, the Mueller name has been associated with dependable water and gas distribution products around the globe. With a foundation of solid core values and a clear mission, Mueller’s International Division is the sales and marketing arm outside of North America for nearly all of the company’s brands and affiliates.View More >








Echologics® Leak Detection and Condition Assessment Services

                        Through its unique technology, service and training curriculum, Echologics provides the most comprehensive and 100% non-invasive leak detection and condition assessment resources. View an overview of its products and services in this section, or visit its web site www.echologics.com.  To purchase or inquire about its products or services, please contact Echologics directly at 1.866.324.6564.View More >








Henry Pratt® Engineered Valves & Actuators

The Henry Pratt Division designs, develops and manufactures butterfly, rectanglular, ball, nuclear, cone, sleeve and energy dissipating valves as well as valve actuators and controls systems.  View an overview of its products in this section, or visit its web site www.henrypratt.com.  To purchase or inquire about its products, please contact Henry Pratt Company directly at 1.630.844.4000 or e-mail marketing@henrypratt.com.View More >








Milliken Valve® Water and Wastewater Valves & Controls

Milliken Valve designs, develops and manufactures plug, check and butterfly valves and their respective controls and actuators for the water, wastewater and industrial markets.  Visit its web site www.millikenvalve.com. To purchase or inquire about its products, please contact Milliken Valve directly at 1.610.861.8803 or e-mail marketing@millikenvalve.com.
 View More >








Hydro-Gate® Water Control Gates

Hydro Gate designs and manufactures slide, weir, hand pull, roller and radial water control gates for a variety of industries, 100% custom built to match customer specific applications.  Visit its web site www.hydrogate.com.  To purchase or inquire about its products, please contact Hydro Gate directly at 1.800.678.8228 or e-mail marketing@hydrogate.com.View More >








Mueller Systems® Smart Metering Solutions

                        Mueller Systems provides Smart Metering solutions to improve conservation, increase efficiencies, reduce non-revenue water and strengthen relationships with customers.  Visit its web site www.muellersystems.com.  To purchase or inquire about its products, please Mueller Systems directly at 1.704.278.2221 or e-mail customercare@muellersystems.com. View More >








Hydro-Guard Flushing & Monitoring Systems

View More >












