Plumbing
Mueller Industries is your single source for a wide array of residential and commercial plumbing products. Our Streamline brand of copper tube and fittings, ABS and PVC fittings, and ABS DWV pipe are preferred by professionals around the world.  In addition we offer today a full line of faucets, plumbing valves and plumbing specialties under our B&K brand.  Our Southland brand is well known for its high quality steel pipe, ready-cut pipe, steel nipples and malleable iron and red brass fittings.  Since the early 1900a's we have been producing the finest plumbing products in the industry. More >



HVAC & Refrigeration
Since 1917 Mueller Industries has been providing our customers with the best products, services, and support in the HVAC/R industry. We invented and pioneered the now famous Streamline solder type copper fitting and Nitrogenized ACR copper tube that have become industry standards. Today, we offer one of the most complete lines of HVAC and Refrigeration products available from single source. Our ongoing commitment to quality and innovation continue to make our products the preferred and specified by industry professionals and manufacturers alike.     More >



Industrial / OEM
Mueller Industries is one of the world's leading manufacturers of copper, brass, plastic, steel, and aluminum products. Mueller Industries offers a wide array of products for industrial end-user applications including brass rod, aluminum forgings, and impact extrusions. We also offer a wide array of engineered products and solutions for original equipment manufactures. 
 More >

       
