Mueller Industries Industrial / OEM — Manufacturing Solutions at Work.
Mueller Industries is one of the world's leading manufacturers of copper, brass, plastic, steel, and aluminum products. Mueller Industries offers a wide array of products for industrial end-user applications including brass rod, aluminum forgings, and impact extrusions. Mueller Industries also offers a wide array of engineered products and solutions for original equipment manufacturers. Our ongoing commitment to quality and innovation continue to make Mueller Industries the preferred and specified brand of industry professionals and manufacturers alike.














     
