Tube & Pipe
Mueller Industries is a global leader of premium-quality tube and pipe for plumbing, air conditioning, refrigeration and other applications. We offer a complete line of US-made Streamline Copper Tube, Plastic-Coated Copper Tube and Line Sets. We also offer a full line of NAFTA approved Steel pipe and Ready Cut pipe under our Southland brand.

