Honours[edit]
Club[edit]

Bayern Munich[183]


Bundesliga: 2009–10, 2012–13, 2013–14, 2014–15, 2015–16, 2016–17
DFB-Pokal: 2009–10, 2012–13, 2013–14, 2015–16
DFL-Supercup: 2010, 2012, 2016
UEFA Champions League: 2012–13
UEFA Super Cup: 2013
FIFA Club World Cup: 2013

Country[edit]

Germany


FIFA World Cup: 2014;[183] Third Place: 2010[184]
UEFA European Championship Semi-finalist: 2012,[185] 2016

Individual[edit]

DFB-Pokal Top Goalscorer: 2009–10 (4 goals), 2013–14 (8 goals)
FIFA World Cup 2010 Man of the Match: vs. England, vs. Uruguay
FIFA World Cup 2014 Man of the Match: vs. Portugal, vs. United States
FIFA World Cup Golden Boot: 2010[150]
FIFA World Cup Best Young Player: 2010[151]
FIFA World Cup 2010 Most assists (3, shared with Mesut Özil, Bastian Schweinsteiger, Kaká, and Dirk Kuyt)
Bayerischer Sportpreis: 2010[186]
Silbernes Lorbeerblatt: 2010,[187] 2014[188]
World Soccer Young Player of the Year: 2010[189]
Bravo Award: 2010[190]
FIFA Ballon d'Or: 15th place 2010, 13th place 2011, 17th place 2013, 5th place 2014,[191] 6th place 2015[192]
ESM Team of the Year: 2012–13[193]
UEFA Best Player in Europe Award: 2013 (6th place), 2014 (4th place), 2016 (10th place)
UEFA Champions League Team of the Group Stage: 2015[194]
FIFA World Cup Silver Ball: 2014[195]
FIFA World Cup Silver Boot: 2014[196]
FIFA World Cup All-Star Team: 2014[197]
FIFA World Cup Dream Team: 2014[198]
Most FIFA World Cups with at least five goals (2010–2014); record shared with Teófilo Cubillas (1970, 1978) & Miroslav Klose (2002–2006)

