    Since our beginning in 1917 as the Mueller Metals Co. and later Mueller Brass Co., Mueller Industries has built a well-earned reputation for offering the finest-quality plumbing, HVAC, refrigeration, and industrial products in the industry.  With manufacturing and distribution facilities located across North America, Great Britain, Mexico, and China, we supply a global audience of wholesalers, retailers, and original equipment manufacturers with the broadest offering of tube, fittings, valves, industrial materials and engineered solutions from a single source.           
